comments: Williams (CHI) brushes Lillard's (MIL) arm and marginal contact occurs as Lillard completes his desired path.
Craig (CHI) is already in Beasley's (MIL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Vucevic (CHI) clamps and holds Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Lillard (MIL) extends his hands forward into DeRozan's (CHI) path and initiates contact that affects DeRozan's SQBR.
Lillard (MIL) brings his hands towards White (CHI) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to receive the pass.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in White's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Williams (CHI) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage and disengage as the pass is delivered.
Williams (CHI) cleanly deflects the ball away from Antetokounmpo (MIL) during his drive.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his forearm towards DeRozan's (CHI) side and marginal contact occurs as DeRozan spins back towards the basket.
Williams (CHI) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Lopez (MIL) continues to move forward into Vucevic (CHI) and delivers contact during the pick.

Replay review of the foul called on Middleton (MIL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Middleton moves laterally into DeRozan's (CHI) path and initiates body to body contact prior to making any contact with the ball.
Craig (CHI) cleanly deflects the ball away from Lillard (MIL).
As Lillard (MIL) regains possession, incidental foot to foot contact occurs with White (CHI).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes a wide screening position in Craig's (CHI) path, and foot to foot contact occurs during the pick.
DeRozan (CHI) jumps forward into Lillard (MIL) and initiates contact prior to the start of Lillard's upward shooting motion.
Middleton (MIL) is moving alongside DeRozan's (CHI) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) contests White's (CHI) shot and marginal contact occurs after the release.
Lillard (MIL) cleanly dislodges the ball from Williams (CHI) as he defends the shot near the rim.
Lopez (MIL) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Williams' (CHI) shot near the rim.
Lopez (MIL) is already in Williams' (CHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Vucevic (CHI) cleanly deflects the ball out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Bucks.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is firming up over his right leg in White's (CHI) path, and he absorbs the contact that occurs during the screen.
Lopez (MIL) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from DeRozan (CHI) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Craig (CHI) initiates contact with Lopez's (MIL) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Lopez (MIL) cleanly blocks White's (CHI) driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Bulls.
Middleton (MIL) moves forward into DeRozan's (CHI) body and delivers contact as he defends the shot near the rim.
Lopez (MIL) is already in Williams' (CHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Vucevic (CHI) moves forward into Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and initiates the body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact from DeRozan (CHI) at the end of the drive.
DeRozan (CHI) initiates contact with Middleton's (MIL) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
White (CHI) swipes his hand down and makes contact with Lillard's (MIL) arm on the perimeter.
